snippet.title: Boots Quest DX (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Buy on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2093950/Boots_Quest_DX
Buy on itch.io: https://discountrealms.itch.io/boots-quest-dx
OST on Bandcamp: https://dragonwarrior.bandcamp.com/album/boots-quest-dx-ost

Boots Quest is an offbeat adventure game about traveling to the ends of the earth in search of the Best Boots. Solve puzzles, complete quests, collect items, and don weird hats as a hapless young boot enthusiast in a compact open world full of strange friends and foes. You can even jump.

Coming to Steam and itch.io on November 25th!
